snippet: Suzann Pettersen won the L.P.G.A.’s Safeway Classic for the second time in three years, taking advantage of her playing partner Yani Tseng’s final-round collapse.
abstract: Suzann Pettersen wins the LPGA’s Safeway Classic for the second time in three years.
